              <span id="reviewTextContainer472056577" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11345481565870427182">The story follows Ichmad, a Palestinian boy and his family. I have never read a book before from a Palestinian perspective, but I&apos;m so glad I have now. This a brutal, and truly heartbreaking read, but I would recommend The Almond Tree to anyone. Amazing book. Well done Michelle for bringing us an alternative perspective.</span>
  <span id="freeText11345481565870427182" style="display:none">The story follows Ichmad, a Palestinian boy and his family. I have never read a book before from a Palestinian perspective, but I'm so glad I have now. This a brutal, and truly heartbreaking read, but I would recommend The Almond Tree to anyone. Amazing book. Well done Michelle for bringing us an alternative perspective.</span>
